    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Indonesian vessels with a very large triangular, usually lateen, sail and a substantial loadbearing outrigger.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
